msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1268
msgid "How do I enable social sharing on BuddyPress activities?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1269
msgid "Social sharing is enabled by default. You can toggle it on/off from the Social Networks tab. Make sure at least one social service is enabled in the services section."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1273
msgid "Can users share activities without being logged in?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1274
msgid "Yes! Enable \"Guest Sharing\" in the Social Networks tab to allow logged-out users to share public activities on social media platforms."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1278
msgid "How do I customize the sharing button appearance?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1279
msgid "Navigate to the Display Settings tab where you can choose from different icon styles (Circle, Rectangle, Black & White, Bar) and customize colors for background, text, and hover states."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1283
msgid "Which social platforms are supported?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1284
msgid "The plugin supports Facebook, X (Twitter), LinkedIn, Pinterest, Reddit, WordPress, Pocket, Telegram, Bluesky, WhatsApp, and Email sharing. You can enable/disable each service individually."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1288
msgid "Can I disable sharing for specific activity types?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1289
msgid "Yes! In the Restrictions tab, you can disable sharing for Blog Posts, User Profiles, and Groups activities."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1293
msgid "How does the reshare functionality work?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1294
msgid "When a user reshares an activity, you can choose to display either just the original activity or the complete activity with nested content. Configure this in the Restrictions tab."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1298
msgid "Do sharing links open in popup windows?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1299
msgid "By default, yes. Social sharing links open in popup windows for a better user experience. You can disable this behavior in the Social Networks tab."
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1303
msgid "Is the plugin compatible with BuddyBoss Platform?"
msgstr ""

#: admin/class-buddypress-share-admin.php:1304
msgid "Yes! The plugin automatically detects and adapts to work with both BuddyPress and BuddyBoss Platform."
msgstr ""

